# c2e6b8c05b324654aa76404a1a2aef9a
msgid "Try a clean install. That is, uninstall calibre, delete :file:`C:\\\\Program Files\\\\Calibre2` (or wherever you previously chose to install calibre). Then re-install calibre. Note that uninstalling does not touch your books or settings."
