msgstr ""

#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/faq.rst:985
# d91c521781f94ec29a86385577210f8c
msgid "If you really, really hate downloading calibre every week but still want to be up to the latest, I encourage you to run from source, which makes updating trivial. Instructions are :ref:`available here <develop>`."
msgstr ""

